node.text:
Holy smokes, the first ever @guysrestaurantreboot presented by @lendingtree was incredible!

Thank you again to all of our amazing chefs including @chefjoseandres @marcuscooks @catcora @guarnaschelli @shaq @gronk @adrianalima @wale @kanebrown_music and dynamite musicians @olddominionmusic and @diplo who joined us! 

Best of all we gave away $300,000 via The Help Rebuild Restaurants Grant to a remarkable group of restaurant owners and entrepreneurs. Special thanks to our presenting partner @lendingtree who has been helping restaurants and small businesses throughout the pandemic. To learn more visit LendingTree.com/reboot
